Title: Quantum oscillator and a bound system of two dyons
Authors: V. M. Ter--Antonyan, A. Nersessian
Comments: 6 pages, LaTeX, corrections in Introduction
Report-no: JINR E2-95-383
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A10 (1995) 2633-2638
\\
  It is shown that $U(1)$--Hamiltonian reduction of a four--dimensional
isotropic quantum oscillator results in a bound system of two spinless
Schwinger's dyons. Its wavefunctions and spectrum are constructed.
